HOW LIVEDATA WORKS:
- It follows the Observer pattern: when we call .postValue(), all active observers are notified.
- It is Lifecycle-aware: it only sends updates to observers (like Activities) that are in an
"active" state (STARTED or RESUMED). This prevents crashes if the UI is destroyed.